<p>I am trying to convert my query columns in rows. This is my query:</p>  <pre class="lang-sql prettyprint-override"><code>select sum(CASE WHEN                       t.price &lt; 5000                 THEN t.price END) AS RANGE1,        sum(CASE WHEN                       t.price between 5000 and 10000                  THEN t.price END) AS RANGE2,        sum(CASE WHEN                       t.price &gt; 10000                 THEN t.price END) AS RANGE3 From       cars t Where       t.status = 3  </code></pre>    <p>The result is like this:</p>  <pre class="lang-SQL prettyprint-override"><code>RANGE1   RANGE2    RANGE3 -------  -------  -------- 50000     75000      84000 </code></pre>    <p>I want the result is as follows:</p>  <pre class="lang-SQL prettyprint-override"><code>RANGE    TOTAL     ------- -------   RANGE1   50000     RANGE2   75000       RANGE3   84000 </code></pre>